entry.content: It has been quite awhile since I have posted, largely because soon after I started my job at Square I had a child! I hope to have some newer blog post soon. But along those lines I want to share a blog post I did with a coworker (Juan Hernandez) for Square that gives a taste of some of the cool data science work we have been up to. This post covers work we did to create a framework for making models interpretable.
